title: *Community proposal #001
body:
@CryptoCrizp -
Lower the emission from 1 Totem per block to 0.3 Totem per block and remove all the unmentioned farm/poles!

TOTEM-FTM (Spiritswap)  40X > 8X
TOTEM-USDC (Spiritswap) 10X > 16X
GRIM-FTM 9.9X > 3.5X
SPIRIT-FTM 8X > 3X
FTM-USDC 6X > 2.5X
HODL-FTM  3.5X > 1X
BSCR-FTM 1.5X > 1X
BUTT-FTM 0.5X > 0.5X

TOTEM Single stake 8X
GRIM Single stake 1X
ZOO Single stake 0.5X
